The precaution of centrists
Matteo Renzi does not participate in the choir calling for Toti's resignation.> Remembering that "we are at the opposition of Toti", the leader of Italy alive emphasizes that "more reason we are guaranteed. We will vote for the judgments. I never thought that a judicial measure should automatically affect the country's political life." Speculation position at Action: "It is too long the list of inquired governors, banged in the newspapers with clamors and then prosciolti or acquitted, from Pittella to Fontana, from Oliverio to De Luca, from Zingaretti to Bonaccini to name a few, not to take with the feet of lead the accusations against Giovanni Toti", says MP Enrico Costa.&nbsp;

