For the Usigrai, the proceedings initiated against Serena Bortone are unacceptable. "And so he did: Roberto Sergio, the man who, as head of Rai, director of the radio, publicly attacked the Giornale Radio Rai on social media, now as managing director fustiga to blows of disciplinary proceedings who, also through social defends his freedom, and professionalism' from a system of control "asphyxiating" on the work of journalists of the Rai", comments on social Daniele Macheda, secretary Usigrai, who adds: "The measures announced on the Scurati affair have therefore arrived but to the wrong person. The disciplinary procedure open to Serena Bortone is unacceptable. That's enough." &nbsp;
